* what aspects of the fight does intelligence affect
= increased chance to pick the better option
= increased chance check for being flanked
= increased chance to retreat from being flanked
= increased chance to keep far away from enemies so he can recover when not on max stamina and spirit
= increased chance to defend rather than attack, after dodging or blocking increased chance to counter attack
= increased chance to dodge a stronger fighter
= increased chance to attack someone with their back turned
= increased chance to attack someone with low stamina
= increased chance to fast retreat from somone on a rampage